OpenHospital

For informations about the software and the original ideas, you can consult the Users manual in the related section
For informations about installation and configuration, you can consult the Admin manual in the related section


Worldwide installations map: https://maps.google.it/maps/ms?msid=216267909530895641148.0004c2e4c293b897b34ab&msa=0


Developed under the GNU GPL license, the project homepage can be found at:
	http://sourceforge.net/projects/openhospital/
and the required files/updates are freely available there.


This program uses the following open source software:
- jasperreports-1.2.0.jar
	see http://jasperforge.org/plugins/project/project_home.php?group_id=102
- jcalendar-1.3.2.jar
	see http://www.toedter.com/en/jcalendar/


OpenHospital has been tested (server side and client side) on:
- Linux (Debian, Ubuntu)
- Windows 7/Vista/XP/2000/2003 Server


